# Prototypical coal to solid fuel layout

Inputs
    Coal: coal_in
    Water: water_in
Outputs
    Solid fuel: solid_out

Boiler
    Inputs
        Water: water_in
        Fuel: solid_out
    Outputs
        Steam: steam

Oil Refinery
    Coal liquefaction
    Inputs
        Coal: coal_in
        Heavy oil: heavy_loop
        Steam: steam
    Outputs
        Heavy oil: heavy_loop
        Light oil: light_oil
        Petroleum: petroleum

Chemical Plant
    Heavy oil cracking
    Modules
        3x Productivity 1
    Inputs
        Heavy oil: heavy_loop
        Water: water_in
    Outputs
        Light oil: light_oil

Chemical Plant
    Solid fuel (Light oil)
    Inputs
        Light oil: light_oil
    Outputs
        Solid fuel: solid_out

Chemical Plant
    Solid fuel (Petroleum)
    Inputs
        Petroleum: petroleum
    Outputs
        Solid fuel: solid_out
